    <h2><%= title %></h2>

    <p>Arthub Flanders is a user-friendly search machine or discovery interface 
    for searching and accessing records which describe cultural heritage 
    objects preserved by the museums of Visual Arts in 
    Flanders. These records are created, edited and managed by the museums who 
    contribute them to this platform.</p>

    <p>The platform enables reuse of these records by museums and third 
    parties in their own (digital) projects.</p>

